title: 1776 Musical Original Broadway Cast (1969)
description:
Although there's already uploaded songs from this musical both on the torrents and on YouTube, NONE of them are from the original Broadway cast recording!  They are all from the movie (sucked) or the 1992 revival, which was OK, but not what made this musical famous.

Guys, I can't upload often because I'm on a monitored ISP, so I only do it for things like Day One or CPAP files, or things that can't be found anywhere else that NEED to be on the torrents.  This needs to be on the torrents.  Anyone who wants to take this as their own and post it as their own upload, PLEASE FEEL FREE TO DO SO!!!  I just want this out there for people to enjoy.
